headline.main: NAZIS SHOW HEAPS OF POLISH PAPERS; Von Moltke Says Carelessness in Warsaw Allowed These Files to Be Recovered MORE WHITE BOOKS LIKELY Berlin Press Continues Acid Comments on Character of American Diplomats
